(122, 2, '2017-06-01 18:55:48', '2017-06-01 18:55:48', '<p class="p1">Anubha and Miatta are friends, travel companions and freelancers carving out a space for themselves in the world. There are many experiences they share and in reflecting on these experiences, one thing becomes clear, while navigating their careers, thinking about starting a family or even finding a living arrangement that best suits their lives, <em><strong>maybe</strong></em> there isn\'t just one way to get it right.</p>', 'Anubha and Miatta', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '33-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-06-01 18:55:48', '2017-06-01 18:55:48', '', 33, 'http://107.180.4.90/~c4c156763514/33-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
