(155, 4, '2017-06-01 20:58:36', '2017-06-01 20:58:36', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">Sylvia and Gary of Smith, Alberta are teenage sweethearts who are about to celebrate their 50</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">th</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> wedding anniversary. They’ve supported each other through life’s ups and downs, but agree there’s one person who’s always been there to pull them through. They can’t imagine their life without her – even if it means being scolded at age 70.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Please visit our SoundCloud page to learn about the musicians who contributed to this piece. </em>', 'Sylvia and Gary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'sylvia-and-gary', '', '', '2017-06-06 14:44:56', '2017-06-06 14:44:56', '', 0, 'http://107.180.4.90/~c4c156763514/?post_type=conversations&#038;p=155', 4, 'conversations', '', 0),
