(179, 3, '2017-06-05 14:52:48', '2017-06-05 14:52:48', '<p class="p1">Mother and daughter, Pearl and Linda are travelling to Ottawa to visit family. Their life-long friend Nancy joins. They’re proud Nova Scotians with a lot to say. But there was one thing that they didn’t want to talk about…</p>\n<p class="p1"><em>Please visit our SoundCloud page for the musicians who contributed to this piece.</em></p>', 'Linda and Pearl and Nancy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '135-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-06-05 14:52:48', '2017-06-05 14:52:48', '', 135, 'http://107.180.4.90/~c4c156763514/135-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
